Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.79,0:00:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Vintage is flying around in the open,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet I must hide myself...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.05,0:00:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Katsuragi{-san} and the others be okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddesses.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.19,0:00:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are present, show yourselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.63,0:00:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we will begin interrogating everyone here, one at a time.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.68,0:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to save these girls, reveal yourselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to start another war?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.18,0:01:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to squeeze my hand so hard?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.20,0:01:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both invisible right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get separated, \Nwe won't be able to find each other again.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.70,0:01:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even know where Ayumi is?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nora's transmitting her location.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's at Seaside Park.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.92,0:01:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:46.97,0:01:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see him.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.32,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsura—
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.92,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, you only have to put up with me a little longer.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.26,0:02:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was {\i1}that{\i0} for?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.27,0:02:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me already!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.84,0:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, why not just tell Ayumi \Nthe truth about what's happening?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.44,0:02:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell the truth, I can't conquer her.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.12,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi's waiting for you to come clean.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the strategy you two devised?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's {\i1}that{\i0} supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was wondering why Ayumi was being so aggressive.{Ayumi ~more aggressive~}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That explains it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.41,0:03:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this ship brings back memories.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.75,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's odd that Vintage hasn't noticed her, \Ngiven our proximity.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, regardless, this will be the stage for the finale.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.73,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katsuragi...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.89,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing a game.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A game where the goal is to seduce you tonight!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But... He has a reason for doing it!{ohshi}{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A reason?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the specifics,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but whatever it is, \Nhe's desperate to see it through.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If this doesn't make sense to you, \Nask him for answers.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to decide on your own \Nwhat you want to do with Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katsuragi, why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It might actually be better to tell her everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure Ayumi would be willing to help.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of ideas.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But on one condition!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I can only answer one question.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to answer one,{ but...}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but your other questions will have to wait.{you can move the 'but' to the above line when timing if it works better that way}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why do {\i1}I{\i0} have to ask questions?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna drag this out?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your question?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I'll answer it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.08,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse to accept this condition, we're done.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never approach you again.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, will you ask me one question?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are we through?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wants to keep the truth from her at all costs?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Tenri?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.74,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... So...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.33,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tenri, why did you not say anything before?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my question.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.81,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.64,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've been lying to me this whole time?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a second question.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.42,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't love me, but you chased me around and proposed to me?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.04,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also a second—
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that I'd {\i1}never{\i0} answer it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to wait—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me {\i1}now{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have a reason for going through all this!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.59,0:06:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need my help, I'll do whatever I can.{ftr this is a tsundere line}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your help.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially not now.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You always insist on doing things your way,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ignoring how everyone else feels!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How could anyone love someone like you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disgusting!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this because I want people to love me.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.94,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only trying to reach the ending.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't require any rewards or assistance.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone else take this responsibility.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a gamer's love.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi, I adore you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my hand,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.75,0:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will guide you to the ending.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.49,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As requested, I tried to make it romantic.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.54,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't take long for them to find us...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ayumi, please come with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this enough?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have a wedding ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.80,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong answer!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you "guess"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything better?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what an ending entails—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to do this, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.15,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I refuse to accept this ending!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too casual about this!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to smile, you sick freak.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.85,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see {\i1}you{\i0} smiling, real girl.{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us exchange vows before the Maijima Sea!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the vows!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like I can trust anything out of {\i1}your{\i0} mouth.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're one nasty bride.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} trust your feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.49,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I decided that if you really came here, \NI would trust you no matter what.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how serious you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what a conquest is at all!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I planned out how to trigger all those flags?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.91,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop talking about conquests for one moment!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, are you two getting married or not?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A conquest is more important than the world!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.46,0:08:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you treat the whole process so lightly!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you take me for?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Back off!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it some serious thought too, you know!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone manipulate my feelings!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.44,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm the one who decided
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to fall in love with you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.42,0:09:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the choice I made, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.32,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand, marry me!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercurius!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Katsuragi{-san}!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana? She has her wings?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.69,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mer, thank you for awakening.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to do something right away.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only just woke up...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Vintage! This is the end of the road!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Loose Souls Team will face you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rimyuel?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, I appreciate your efforts in this endeavor.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.64,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Some members of the Loose Souls Team still refuse to give in to Vintage.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come to show them what we're made of.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.18,0:10:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We will rescue the captive girls.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us take it from here.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay together!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We will help reunite the goddesses!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that Akari?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.83,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.61,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. 
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done my part.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that thing inside Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.45,0:11:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It grew wings and flew off.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.97,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.26,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see a thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.64,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.23,0:11:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a concert to prepare for.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for us to just leave?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.08,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.91,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing more we can do to help.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why are you coming with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I left my guitar at your house!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't play in the concert without it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's up...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. This was what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you trying to creep me out?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.12,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to bring out \NAyumi's goddess thanks to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.61,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything I could to screw it up!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't tell her about Hell.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had, it would have taken much longer.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.60,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand what was going on.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.52,0:12:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you had to worry about protecting me
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when I wasn't even supposed to be involved.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Those shadowy figures were after Ayumi, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to do with any of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sorry you had to protect me.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the winds are changing.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You put up a good fight.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you live this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.48,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi's sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{x}Miss Nikaidou{-sensei}?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's safe for you to go.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be late for your band's performance.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I had to say.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? O-Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did {x}Miss Nikaidou{-sensei} say that?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.01,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm Kanon{-chan} right now!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How did she know it was me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.32,0:14:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why did you go on a date with me
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,on Festival Eve?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.58,0:14:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't go on a date for no reason, would you?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.77,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something inside me?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something inside me as well?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.02,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You weren't involved in all that.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that's a relief!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd suck if I were actually involved in this mess.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.57,0:15:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I never have to talk to you again.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.07,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, I'll be listening to your performance today.{;_;}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be blown away!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.82,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.94,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,10,,Ellie, Yui, and Ayumi are all missing!{lower margin}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're running late?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to start without them.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real show!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our first on-stage performance!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When's Kanon{-chan} performing?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.05,0:16:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more band left.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you feel the earthquake this morning?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, the next band is up!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.48,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the 2B Pencils!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.77,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our first concert,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.78,0:17:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but something came up, and three of our members couldn't make it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.96,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Running late?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill them!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'll just be the two of us!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.86,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they know what they're doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The pick...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.89,0:17:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, please listen to our song!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Chihiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a little late...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.02,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit talking{,} and get changed already!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us a moment!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that dress? \NDid you get married or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do the right thing?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what you mean,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but whatever it is, you decided it yourself, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.93,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your guitar out!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.75,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try this again.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.32,0:18:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the 2B Pencils!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you could all make it!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to be late to your own concert!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.62,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.96,0:18:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's a part of the festival, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mai High Festival's almost over.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you all have a good time?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.34,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're here, \Nlet's make some great memories!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's someone you like, tell them how you feel!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.55,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon{-chan}?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kanon{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's she here?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.34,0:19:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chihiro{-san}.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I sing with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{No way. Get lost.}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.47,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You once said that you wanted to have a contest with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to sing with you!{dem cannons}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.05,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't what I meant to say back then.{;_;}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:49.31,0:22:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,El{-chan}!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.02,0:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A customer gave me these cyclamens.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:55.04,0:22:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're so pretty!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they lovely?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We should put them in the café!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.41,0:23:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been five days since then.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:08.21,0:23:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The members of Vintage were all arrested,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.36,0:23:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and their plan to revive Old Hell came to an end.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.26,0:23:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haqua was reinstated at the Loose Souls Team—
Dialogue: 5,0:23:20.50,0:23:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:23.69,0:23:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fired, Haqua?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A lot of stuff happened, okay?{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also, in recognition of her help in defeating Vintage,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:29.88,0:23:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nora was promoted to Head Section Chief.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just wrong!{well, it was part of the agreement!}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.57,0:23:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my Exalted Brother...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is back to normal.
